quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  110,1,"When there comes the Help of Allah (to you, O Muhammad against your enemies) and the victory (of Makkah)"
  110,2,and you see the people entering in Allah’s religion (Islam) in crowds
  110,3,"So glorify the praises of your Lord, and ask for His forgiveness. Surely, He is the one who accepts repentance (and forgives)"